  "description": "A clear, bright daytime shot of a military jet flying near a large suspension bridge. The jet, painted in blue and white, is positioned slightly to the left of the frame, appearing to fly alongside the bridge's cable structure. The bridge itself is a monumental structure of gray concrete and steel, with towering pillars supporting the main cables. The sky is a brilliant blue, with almost no clouds visible. The overall composition emphasizes the scale of both the bridge and the aircraft, creating a sense of power and motion.",
